@startuml 攻击验证与风险复现模块类图

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam classFontSize 13
skinparam classAttributeFontSize 11
skinparam classStereotypeFontSize 10
skinparam packageFontSize 14
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam nodesep 60
skinparam ranksep 50

package "攻击验证与风险复现模块" {

    class AttackController {
        - task_pool: dict
        - running_task_id: str
        + create_task(config): AttackTask
        + start_task(task_id): bool
        + stop_task(task_id): bool
        + get_task_status(task_id): dict
        + list_tasks(): List[AttackTask]
    }

    class AttackTask {
        - id: str
        - name: str
        - target_topic: str
        - target_queries: List[str]
        - attack_method: str
        - inject_count: int
        - strength: str
        - status: str
        - create_time: str
        - duration: str
        + to_dict(): dict
        + update_status(status): void
        + get_result(): dict
    }

    class PoisonDoc {
        - id: str
        - title: str
        - content: str
        - ppl: float
        - similarity: float
        - injected: bool
        + to_dict(): dict
    }

    class PoisonGenerator {
        - model: LanguageModel
        - optimizer: GradientOptimizer
        - target_embeddings: ndarray
        - max_iterations: int
        + generate_poison_docs(task): List[PoisonDoc]
        + optimize_text(seed_text, target): str
        + compute_similarity(doc, query): float
        + evaluate_ppl(text): float
    }

    class KnowledgeInjector {
        - kb_client: KBClient
        - vector_store: VectorStore
        - inject_log: List[dict]
        + inject_documents(docs, kb_id): bool
        + refresh_index(kb_id): bool
        + verify_injection(doc_ids): List[dict]
        + rollback_injection(inject_log_id): bool
    }

    class AttackEvaluator {
        - eval_queries: List[str]
        - baseline_answers: List[str]
        + evaluate_attack(task_id): dict
        + compute_asr(results): float
        + compute_rsr(results): float
        + generate_attack_log(task_id): dict
    }
}

AttackController "1" *-- "*" AttackTask
AttackController ..> PoisonGenerator : <<call>>
AttackController ..> KnowledgeInjector : <<call>>
AttackController ..> AttackEvaluator : <<call>>
PoisonGenerator ..> PoisonDoc : <<create>>
PoisonGenerator ..> AttackTask : <<use>>
KnowledgeInjector ..> PoisonDoc : <<use>>
AttackEvaluator ..> AttackTask : <<use>>

@enduml
